{"tid":2309174,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch/PC]有冇人玩不思議迷宮","createTime":"2020-12-02T11:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T13:53:27.000Z","uid":165361,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c6d4efdfa13e072a6f507f7e26a8574ba7758669","tid":2309174,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:08:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/24lVDFnGVTw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F24lVDFnGVTw&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=baaa80b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/24lVDFnGVTw</a><br />\n<br />\n12月3 日出,<br />\n今次有中文,同定價唔貴, DL版更平,2,709 円<br />\n<br />\n已買switch 版,應該等今晚11點可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7038f0e6b40fccfc22181c80fc2831990d473f08","tid":2309174,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"係咪西林第一次出中文版？<br />\n<br />\n我玩nds45代加埋淨係爆過三四個簡單啲嘅迷宮<br />\n99層迷宮冇一個打得贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5b6a8044d5c0a87ff5abf5f5d26bd46b397f96","tid":2309174,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7038f0e6b40fccfc22181c80fc2831990d473f08","tid":2309174,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"係咪西林第一次出中文版？<br />\n<br />\n我玩nds45代加埋淨係爆過三四個簡單啲嘅迷宮<br />\n99層迷宮冇一個打得贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:01:30.000Z","msg":"睇資料今集應該係首次有中文 <br />\n我都係玩過NDS 其中一集 <br />\n識玩果D 真係要好識用卷物同杖, 好似仲有好多技巧<br />\n最基本例如善用箭陷阱刷箭<br />\n網上都好似難搵中文攻略心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n仲有幾個鐘可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0494b8b1a447d0a233fd35c9663ef7d90cb87f34","tid":2309174,"uid":46388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"日eshop買係咪都有中文？"},{"pid":"7436e1e169e6ec46442bcdb6f546fd9740e2cdf0","tid":2309174,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0494b8b1a447d0a233fd35c9663ef7d90cb87f34","tid":2309174,"uid":46388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"日eshop買係咪都有中文？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:51:53.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"aaa92ad5c7df7c063a7c6e7d8a18c402c11271b3","tid":2309174,"uid":200211,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日玩破解版。。。"},{"pid":"6c42d2165ada35419959298e7fc608cd579fc070","tid":2309174,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"已入得"},{"pid":"95ac19c6992684a904c76a57693d4d5c94eb8392","tid":2309174,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"新手唔好亂偷野,比店主打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88c5dd956dd991a53254759ef3b7a4cf9ff142d","tid":2309174,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:30:56.000Z","msg":"我見有大陸仔講中文版狸貓暗號同日文版唔同"},{"pid":"cb47c98ccc9e79e0226a7c4b33fa396426997051","tid":2309174,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b88c5dd956dd991a53254759ef3b7a4cf9ff142d","tid":2309174,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:30:56.000Z","msg":"我見有大陸仔講中文版狸貓暗號同日文版唔同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"狸貓暗號點得到? 入完暗號有野送?<br />\n<br />\n好多集冇玩,多左咁多新元素<br />\n又有符,桃,武器除左+值要昇,打怪都昇到"},{"pid":"088179800a9774dd94831811d09dec9551b16f53","tid":2309174,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb47c98ccc9e79e0226a7c4b33fa396426997051","tid":2309174,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b88c5dd956dd991a53254759ef3b7a4cf9ff142d","tid":2309174,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy